This product retrieves drone geozone and aeronautical weather data from
the German "Digitale Plattform Unbemannte Luftfahrt" (DIPUL) and DFS
Deutsche Flugsicherung GmbH services, and general weather data from
Open-Meteo (https://open-meteo.com). These services are not affiliated
with this project and retain all rights to their respective data.
